column4: NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "E4955B4D411190D559F904B2F52F0708", "So we meet again. Do you have a request?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "5786772B4510641E4A93AC8164DA0B06", "What the... oh no! It\'s the Lake Guardian!")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "E7EDF5B442E03D14FE6EA8A2E35550A9", "So you are the one who\'s been fishing so much! So be it. Any requests?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "B75E4A9E48B9BB8730EC049C207353D3", "What!? I see why they call you Guardian. Yes, I have a request.")

column13: ((17, NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "C0DB0586431549A8D5A64296E708FD44", "Let\'s be friends")),(36, NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "4091F9C14B5449436F246EB0040FCBF7", "Teach me a Technique")),(51, NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "44376DD24FB92FA0231FDAB320759E77", "I want an Item")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "80654C6941D8077E292EBE9AE320E56D", "We\'re friends from now on. I give you this flute as proof.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "AD5B16724DD9337286ABADBACD5DB4E8", "Oh no! Too many Items. I need to throw some away.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "25CD8B94465E258D598052B789C00440", "If you play the flute near the lake, I\'ll come. I\'ll take you to the other side.")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "019DEA5849C8EC7EA1CCE7983C3B9BBC", "You mean I can go to the other side? Thanks!")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "3C5F42224B207A26EFACDE93AA5076FC", "Beyond the lake, there is a strange forest. Do you want go there right now?")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "45C0EF38454621AD706EDBB7A0953E73", "Uh, I don\'t think there are any more Techniques I can teach you...")
NSLOCTEXT("[6DA7FBC34688C00C2B3311BE2A399469]", "AD5B16724DD9337286ABADBACD5DB4E8", "Oh no! Too many Items. I need to throw some away.")
